sequenceDiagram
  actor User as User
  participant FE as Forge Page
  participant NA as NextAuth
  participant BE as Next.js API
  participant AI as Gemini AI

  User->>FE: Upload PDF / PPTX
  FE->>FE: Extract text locally
  FE->>NA: Verify session token
  NA-->>FE: Valid session
  FE->>BE: POST /api/generate
  BE->>AI: generateContent(prompt)
  AI-->>BE: Return JSON questions
  BE-->>FE: Send parsed quiz array
  FE-->>User: Render interactive quiz
